= Use Custom Color Schemes
:revdate: 2020-10-24

Windows Terminal allows using customizing color schemes.

== Get Custom Color Schemes

link:https://windowsterminalthemes.dev[windowsterminalthemes.dev] provides a collection of Windows Terminal Color schemes ready to be pased into `settings.json`.

== _Snazzy_ Theme

I currently use the link:https://windowsterminalthemes.dev/?theme=Snazzy[_Snazzy_ Theme] for Windows Terminal.

